HEADWORD: Synthesize
<hw>Syn"the*size</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
combine by synthesis; to unite.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To produce by synthesis; <as>as, to
<ex>synthesize</ex> albumin</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

